    "body": "I'm not sure if this is the solution? I'm facing the same issue here.\r\nYou would expect to see:\r\n- All menu levels in the refinement (\"Digital Camera's\" and \"Digital SLR Camera's\") When clicking on digital SLR camera's the parent selection still must be selected.\r\nOR\r\n- when you only show the deepest menu, and click on it, go back to the parent menu, and not to the root.\r\n\r\nOn both options you still have to clear the current menu, and not the whole menu. So going back to the parent item.",
