    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For the moment this is the behaviour we have inside all the InstantSearch flavour (JS, React, Vue, Angular). To support the proposed solution it does not require a lot of work but it would change the default behaviour and it won't be backward compatible. I don't think it bring value to add an option to support this feature since it can be implemented with the connector API (or even with a [`breadcrumb`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/breadcrumb.html)). So it's either we keep what we have now or we change the implementation for your suggestion. I've open [an issue](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/3346) to discuss that with the team.",
