    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "How to achieve this with the connectCurrentRefinedValues then? Since we use this already, but i can only find the lvl.0 in the refinements. using [js example](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/dev/app/jquery/widgets/currentRefinedValues.js)\r\n\r\nAnd breadcrumb is another UX item ofcourse, which we already use, but aint the functionallity of a clear filter.\r\n\r\nAlso the hierachical menu itself has a strange way of (de)selecting a parent item. Using v3 [example](https://v3--instantsearchjs.netlify.com/stories/?selectedStory=CurrentRefinements.with%20hierarchicalMenu) You/I would also expect here when you click on \"Camera's & Camcorders\" it would go to that menu-item, now it also goes to the root, so it doesn't functional as a menu but as a checkbox on/off",
